### HomeBase Crypto Bot API - REST Client Tests
### Use VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Ctrl+Alt+R to run request | Ctrl+Alt+E to switch environment

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api
@coingeckoUrl = https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Health Check
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/health HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Crypto Price API (Local Azure Function)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get default prices (BTC, ETH, SOL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto HTTP/1.1

### Get specific coins
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,cardano,solana,dogecoin HTTP/1.1

### Get prices in multiple currencies
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd,eur,gbp HTTP/1.1

### Get minimal response (no market cap/24h change)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin,ethereum&include_market_cap=false&include_24hr_change=false HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Direct CoinGecko API (for comparison/reference)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### CoinGecko Ping (test API availability)
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/ping HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - Simple Price
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/simple/price?ids=bitcoin,ethereum&vs_currencies=usd HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - Trending coins (great for discovery)
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/search/trending HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - Top 10 by market cap
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/coins/markets?vs_currency=usd&order=market_cap_desc&per_page=10&page=1 HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - Bitcoin detailed info
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/coins/bitcoin HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### CoinGecko - Historical chart data (7 days)
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/coins/bitcoin/market_chart?vs_currency=usd&days=7 HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - OHLC candle data (1 day)
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/coins/bitcoin/ohlc?vs_currency=usd&days=1 HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Staking & DeFi Research Endpoints
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### CoinGecko - Global DeFi data
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/global/decentralized_finance_defi HTTP/1.1

### CoinGecko - Exchange rates for staking calc
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/exchange_rates HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Meme Coins & High-Volatility Tracking
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Popular meme coins
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/simple/price?ids=dogecoin,shiba-inu,pepe,floki,bonk&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true HTTP/1.1

### Coins with highest 24h gains (requires Pro API)
# GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/coins/markets?vs_currency=usd&order=percent_change_24h_desc&per_page=10 HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Testing Rate Limits & Error Handling
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Invalid coin ID (should return empty object)
GET {{coingeckoUrl}}/simple/price?ids=fake-coin-xyz&vs_currencies=usd HTTP/1.1

### Test caching - Run twice quickly (second should be cached)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🤖 AUTONOMOUS BOT SYSTEM API
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all bots and their status
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots HTTP/1.1

### Get market overview (majors, gainers, losers, trending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/market HTTP/1.1

### Get recent signals from bot runs
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/signals HTTP/1.1

### Get signals filtered by coin
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/signals?coin=bitcoin&limit=10 HTTP/1.1

### Get technical analysis for Bitcoin
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/analysis/bitcoin HTTP/1.1

### Get technical analysis for Ethereum
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/analysis/ethereum HTTP/1.1

### Get technical analysis for Solana
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/analysis/solana HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🚀 Manual Bot Triggers (Run strategies on-demand)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Run Price Alert strategy
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/price-alert HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin", "ethereum", "solana", "cardano", "dogecoin"]
}

### Run Opportunity Detector
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/opportunity HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin", "ethereum", "solana", "avalanche-2", "polkadot"]
}

### Run SMA Crossover analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/sma HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin", "ethereum", "solana"]
}

### Run Arbitrage Scanner for Bitcoin
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/arbitrage HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin"]
}

### Run Arbitrage Scanner for Ethereum
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/arbitrage HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["ethereum"]
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📊 Full Analysis Workflow
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Step 1: Get market overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/market HTTP/1.1

### Step 2: Run opportunity detector on top coins
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/opportunity HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin", "ethereum", "solana", "cardano", "avalanche-2"]
}

### Step 3: Get detailed analysis on promising coin
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/analysis/bitcoin HTTP/1.1

### Step 4: Check for arbitrage opportunity
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run/arbitrage HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coins": ["bitcoin"]
}

### Step 5: Review all signals
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/signals HTTP/1.1
